CRYSTALWISE TECH said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 41.50% to NT$158,051,000 from NT$270,183,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales            158,051          270,183    
YOY%             -41.50%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            519,746         1,181,595   
YOY%             -56.01% 
